{"data":[{"id":"36_1753853355.26","type":"feed","offset":36,"verb":"TOPIC_ACKNOWLEDGED_ANSWER","created_time":1753853355,"updated_time":1753853355,"target":{"id":"1933486577809589356","type":"answer","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/answers/1933486577809589356","author":{"id":"806385eda45bf8d6b7156b2a79e0a48f","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/people/806385eda45bf8d6b7156b2a79e0a48f","user_type":"people","url_token":"milkfly-20","name":"milkfly","headline":"真相不为意志所转移，一直在那里。","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-d5fd2186a73ed919fd19892ed66c261b_l.jpg?source=b6762063","is_org":false,"gender":0,"followers_count":7177,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false},"created_time":1753759122,"updated_time":1753762211,"voteup_count":125,"thanks_count":4,"comment_count":27,"is_copyable":true,"question":{"id":"1933204871273740236","type":"question","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/1933204871273740236","author":{"id":"d371683fd9673e521609ae7a4788e856","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/people/d371683fd9673e521609ae7a4788e856","user_type":"people","url_token":"bo-ben-er-ba-26","name":"liisu","headline":"路人甲","avatar_url":"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-d24ffbc4102e48b6f12d8996682207ae_l.jpg?source=b6762063","is_org":false,"gender":-1,"followers_count":1485,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false},"title":"科大讯飞董事长称马斯克不懂 AI，疑遭私募大佬但斌怒怼，这场争论的焦点是什么？科大讯飞AI技术怎么样？","created":1753691958,"answer_count":0,"follower_count":0,"comment_count":0,"bound_topic_ids":[350,1740,2143,6381,1952454],"is_following":false,"excerpt":"","relationship":{"is_author":false},"detail":"","question_type":"normal"},"excerpt":"好久好久以前……那时候世界上绝大部份人还不知道AI是什么东西， 黄仁勋做出一台AI超算却乏人问津，当时却有一家新创公司洽询， “我们可以要一台吗？” 黄仁勋闻讯大喜，并将机器搬上自己的家用车，亲自开车送货上门。 那台机器是世界第一台AI超算DGX-1。 拿到这台机器的公司就是现在叱咤风云的open AI。 而当是默默无闻的open AI的联合创始人名单中，有一个大家都认识的人， 他的名字叫“埃伦 马斯克”，他同时也是如今X AI的C…","excerpt_new":"好久好久以前……那时候世界上绝大部份人还不知道AI是什么东西， 黄仁勋做出一台AI超算却乏人问津，当时却有一家新创公司洽询， “我们可以要一台吗？” 黄仁勋闻讯大喜，并将机器搬上自己的家用车，亲自开车送货上门。 那台机器是世界第一台AI超算DGX-1。 拿到这台机器的公司就是现在叱咤风云的open AI。 而当是默默无闻的open AI的联合创始人名单中，有一个大家都认识的人， 他的名字叫“埃伦 马斯克”，他同时也是如今X AI的C…","preview_type":"default","preview_text":"","reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp data-pid=\"vaAiv_y4\"\u003e好久好久以前……那时候世界上绝大部份人还不知道AI是什么东西，\u003cbr/\u003e黄仁勋做出一台AI超算却乏人问津，当时却有一家新创公司洽询，\u003cbr/\u003e“我们可以要一台吗？”\u003cbr/\u003e黄仁勋闻讯大喜，并将机器搬上自己的家用车，亲自开车送货上门。\u003cbr/\u003e那台机器是世界第一台AI超算DGX-1。\u003cbr/\u003e拿到这台机器的公司就是现在叱咤风云的open AI。\u003cbr/\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e而当是默默无闻的open AI的\u003cb\u003e联合创始人\u003c/b\u003e名单中，有一个大家都认识的人，\u003cbr/\u003e他的名字叫“\u003cb\u003e埃伦 马斯克\u003c/b\u003e”，他同时也是如今X AI的CEO。\u003cbr/\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e从遥遥领先，再到清场式遥遥领先…继之而来加上了人参公鸡，\u003cbr/\u003e先\u003cb\u003e是马斯克不懂AI\u003c/b\u003e，\u003cbr/\u003e而后估计会是……\u003cbr/\u003e马斯克\u003cb\u003e不懂电车\u003c/b\u003e，\u003cbr/\u003e马斯克\u003cb\u003e不懂卫星\u003c/b\u003e，\u003cbr/\u003e马斯克\u003cb\u003e不懂火箭，\u003cbr/\u003e\u003c/b\u003e马斯克\u003cb\u003e不懂生小孩！\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"is_thanked":false,"is_nothelp":false,"voting":0},"is_labeled":false,"visited_count":10383,"favorite_count":8,"answer_type":"normal","is_navigator":false,"navigator_vote":false,"vote_next_step":"vote"},"brief":"{\"source\": \"TS\", \"type\": \"answer\", \"id\": 1933486577809589356}","attached_info":"","action_card":false},{"id":"37_1753853355.572","type":"feed","offset":37,"verb":"TOPIC_ACKNOWLEDGED_ANSWER","created_time":1753853355,"updated_time":1753853355,"target":{"id":"1906658230274352478","type":"answer","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/answers/1906658230274352478","author":{"id":"51db049c2dd4beb6e5ddccd7d45c856b","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/people/51db049c2dd4beb6e5ddccd7d45c856b","user_type":"people","url_token":"tian-liang-45-72","name":"天天天蓝","headline":"读书","avatar_url":"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-35f0e0bf64c7e1b54f6fcc12aaaedb48_l.jpg?source=b6762063","is_org":false,"gender":1,"followers_count":2010,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false},"created_time":1747362746,"updated_time":1747362746,"voteup_count":18352,"thanks_count":745,"comment_c